  1,Port has not been opened yet
  2,Cannot open the port
  3,Cannot obtain communication error
  4,Cannot get the state of the port
  5,Cannot set the state of the port
  6,Break timing error
  7,Cannot place the transmission line in a break state
  8,Cannot place the transmission line in a nonbreak state
  9,Cannot set the timeouts for the port
  10,Cannot clear the port
  11,Error reading data from the port
  12,Error writing data to the port
  13,Cannot get the control lines of the port
  14,Error setting the control lines of the port
  15,Error reading the status lines of the port
